{"tid":522850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無限復活]高院頒令撤銷清盤申請　亞視正式「復活」","createTime":"2018-01-08T02:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T06:42:23.000Z","uid":389,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4dc2c3ca9594a5bb9c4ca0661934c0be698015","tid":522850,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/104952_07d601d81bbe0cc18285d65bda37cc83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F104952_07d601d81bbe0cc18285d65bda37cc83.png&h=4d5c7d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已「熄機」逾一年的亞洲電視有限公司，前年被其前主要投資者兼最大債權人王征入稟申請清盤，星鉑企業有限公司從王征購入債項後，成為最大債權人。星鉑上月向高院申請為亞視進行債務重組，獲法庭批准。高院今頒令撤銷亞視清盤申請，意味亞視正式「復活」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180108/s00001/1515377788927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180108%2Fs00001%2F1515377788927&d=Obgldri6mh5%2FSbhtWCMOBm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f2e3491d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180108%2Fs00001%2F1515377788927&h=da42f678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180108/s00001/1515377788927</a>"},{"pid":"910dfbc6a04180a9ef7bb9e15310943d24c4e587","tid":522850,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"亞視永恆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3468fe289c7d4c007acbfd34ff73d1aa0e9825","tid":522850,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"老是打不死"},{"pid":"ad259c2a6a58c6a9fe949cb7f39e5c69503ad78c","tid":522850,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"